name: Geek Bar Pulse 15,000 Puffs Disposable 16mL
description:
Geek Bar Pulse 15,000 Puffs Disposable

Famed manufacturer Geek Bar revolutionizes the disposables game with their new 15,000 Puffs device (yes you read that right), Geek Bar Pulse. This unique new disposable is tailor made for your ideal vaping experience with two adjustable modes that alter the power of its hit. Mode 1 provides more immediate sensation at 7500 puffs while Mode 2 delivers longer lasting pleasures at 15,000 puffs. Unlike anything that's come out before, be sure to stay ahead of the curve, by having your finger directly on the pulse.

  • Watermelon Ice

description:
Geek Bar Pulse X 25000 Puffs Disposable

What do you call the successor of the disposable vape that's already been the next big thing? Probably the Geek Bar Pulse X 25000 Puffs Disposable. Advancing upon the specs of the original Geek Bar Pulse, Pulse X boasts two different power modes: Regular and Pulse with 25,000 and 15,000 puffs for each mode respectively. The device notably also features a 3D Curved Indicator Screen featuring the constellation designs made iconic on the original edition, the first of its kind for any vape device. Whether you're a tried and true fan of Geek Bar Pulse or simply seeking a new high-powered disposable, Geek Bar Pulse X is just for you.

name: Geek Bar Pulse Mintz Edition 15,000 Puffs
description:
Geek Bar Pulse Mintz Edition 15,000 Puffs

The Geek Bar Pulse has certainly made a name for itself. And for good reason. They are well-known for their delicious flavors and very consistent and reliable products. Even when the world moves onto 40k or even 50k puff counts, the 15k puff count of Geek Bar Pulse is still one of the hottest and highest selling products on the market. 

Now, you can enjoy the same craftiness in quality, with a minty twist. You have to check out the Geek Bar Pulse Mintz Edition 15,000 Puffs Disposable. 

Flavors:

  • IceyMintz - The IceyMintz Geek Bar Pulse offers an intensely cool and frosty mint flavor that refreshes the senses with every inhale. Perfectly crafted for those who enjoy an icy kick, this flavor delivers a crisp and invigorating Mintz Edition Flavor.  Enjoy the coolest and most refreshing mint flavor yet with the Icey Mintz Geek Bar Pulse. 
  • CreamyMintz - The CreamyMintz Geek Bar Pulse flavor debuted with the Christmas Edition Geek Bar Pulse X. Creamy Mintz was inspired by the after dinner mint with the jellied core. A delightful vape flavor and a long overdue addition to the many mint disposable vape flavors.  Inspired by those delicious mints with the creamy, jellied center, Creamy Mintz Geek Bar Pulse is the ultimate creamy mint vape. 
  • BlackMintz - A bold and invigorating fusion of blackcurrant and mint. The sweet and slightly tart taste of ripe blackcurrants pairs seamlessly with a refreshing burst of mint.  Perfect for vapers who enjoy a fruity twist with a cooling effect, offering a balanced mix of sweet, tangy, and minty sensations.
  • StoneMintz - The StoneMintz Geek Bar Pulse is an especially clean and cold mint flavor. It combines the earthy tones of natural mint with a smooth, refreshing finish. StoneMintz provides the glacial chill that adult vapers love in the reliable and powerful Geek Bar Pulse
  • PepperMintz - The red and white striped peppermint confection provided inspiration for the crisp, refreshing and cool Peppermintz Geek Bar Pulse.   The PepperMintz Geek Bar Pulse delivers a bold and refreshing peppermint flavor with every puff, leaving a cool and invigorating sensation. The flavor is patterned after a hook-shaped Christmas candied cane or red and white after dinner mint. This makes sense as the flavor debuted with the Geek Bar Pulse X in their Christmas Edition. 

Features:

  • 15,000 Puffs (Mode 2)
  • 7,500 Puffs (Mode 1)
  • 5% available Nicotine
  • Dual Mesh Coil
